com.interpss.core.acsc

Interface Acsc3WBranch

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Aclf3WBranch, Branch, Branch3W, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclf3WXfrAdaptation, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DStab3WBranch
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Acsc3WBranchImpl, DStab3WBranchImpl

    public interface Acsc3WBranch
extends Aclf3WBranch
    A representation of the model object 'Acsc3 WBranch'. Acsc 3-winding branch

    The following features are supported:

    • From Grounding
    • To Grounding
    • Tertary Grounding
    See Also:
    AcscPackage.getAcsc3WBranch()
